column16: Alex Dickerson triples (1) on a sharp line drive to right fielder Yasiel Puig.   Yangervis Solarte scores.    Derek Norris scores.
Hyun-Jin Ryu intentionally walks Derek Norris.
Yangervis Solarte doubles (13) on a sharp ground ball to left fielder Scott Van Slyke.   Matt Kemp scores.
Matt Kemp doubles (21) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Trayce Thompson.
Wil Myers pops out to shortstop Corey Seager.
Melvin Upton Jr.   bunt grounds out, pitcher Hyun-Jin Ryu to first baseman Adrian Gonzalez.
Drew Pomeranz strikes out on a foul tip.
Ryan Schimpf flies out to center fielder Trayce Thompson.   Alexei Ramirez to 3rd.
Alexei Ramirez doubles (14) on a line drive to left fielder Scott Van Slyke.   Derek Norris scores.
Alex Dickerson grounds out, second baseman Howie Kendrick to first baseman Adrian Gonzalez.   Derek Norris to 3rd.
Derek Norris singles on a sharp ground ball to shortstop Corey Seager.  Derek Norris advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by shortstop Corey Seager.
Matt Kemp grounds out, third baseman Justin Turner to first baseman Adrian Gonzalez.
Wil Myers flies out to left fielder Scott Van Slyke.
Melvin Upton Jr.   grounds into a force out, shortstop Corey Seager to second baseman Howie Kendrick.   Drew Pomeranz out at 2nd.
Drew Pomeranz singles on a ground ball to center fielder Trayce Thompson.   Alex Dickerson scores.    Alexei Ramirez to 2nd.
Alexei Ramirez singles on a line drive to center fielder Trayce Thompson.   Alex Dickerson to 2nd.
